game.name: Toto in the Frozen Land
game.description: You are greatly needed in... Frozen Land, you know! That is right, poor little Sisi being held hostage there by some evil snowball monsters and her best friend, Toto, the adorable little pinky pup, is getting ready to embark on a rescuing adventure. He could not be the hero that he dreams to be without your help, so go ahead and help him skillfully jump from one suspended platform to another, bravely face all those devilish monsters and collect as many of the valuable coins (and THE precious key to Sisi holding cell door, too) scattered there!
